QuestData.Title: Monkey Business
QuestData.Description: We've got major problems with the monkeys in the jungle to the east. They've stolen all of our explosives, and now they're going around throwing them.$B$BSometimes at us!$B$BI had Fizz Lighter take some of his nitro and put it in these bananas. No monkey can resist a bunch of bananas!$B$BAll you have to do is go out there and feed them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Feed 10 Bomb-Throwing Monkeys by tossing Nitro-Potassium Bananas to them.
QuestData.RewardText: They launched up into the air when they ate the bananas?! That is hilarious!$B$BI think I'm going to take a bunch out there and feed them myself!
